msgid "Upstream Servers"
msgstr "上游伺服器"

msgid ""
"Upstream Servers, support UDP, TCP protocol. Please configure multiple DNS "
"servers, including multiple foreign DNS servers."
msgstr ""
"上游 DNS 伺服器，支援 UDP、TCP 協定。請設定多個上游 DNS 伺服器，包括多個國內"
"外伺服器。"

msgid "Use Proxy"
msgstr "使用代理伺服器"

msgid "Use proxy to connect to upstream DNS server."
msgstr "使用代理伺服器來連線上游 DNS 伺服器。"

msgid ""
"Used to verify the validity of the TLS server, The value is Base64 encoded "
"SPKI fingerprint, leaving blank to indicate that the validity of TLS is not "
"verified."
msgstr ""
"用於校驗 TLS 伺服器的有效性，數值為 Base64 編碼的 SPKI 指紋，留空表示不驗證 "
"TLS 的合法性。"

msgid "Write cache to disk on exit and load on startup."
msgstr "退出時儲存 cache 到磁碟，啟動時載入。"

